      • getHqlConstraint

        public abstract String getHqlConstraint()
        Get an HQL constraint that will be used to match this credential to one in the database based on the identifying characteristics of this credential. See PrincipalDAO.savePrincipal(Principal) for usage. The credential entity should be referenced using alias "cred" in the constraint.
        Returns:
        an HQL constraint (never should be empty or null)
